Three people are arrested in China's Guangdong Province in relation to a $90 million gold heist, the biggest in Hong Kong history. (Radio Australia)Former U.S. vice-president Dick Cheney is charged over a bribery scheme involving oil services company Halliburton by Nigeria's anti-corruption agency. The charges relate to when he was the company's top executive. (Al Jazeera) (AFP via The Sydney Morning Herald)